{
  "video_id": "xpBgMYj7aTo",
  "title": "Is it a crime to drive with an \"open container\"?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6160.0,
      "end_time": 10150.0,
      "text": "California law makes it illegal to drive with an open container"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10150.0,
      "end_time": 11700.0,
      "text": "of alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11700.0,
      "end_time": 14430.0,
      "text": "Now, in order to be cited for open container,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14430.0,
      "end_time": 17689.0,
      "text": "the police do not have to prove that you were drunk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17690.0,
      "end_time": 21160.0,
      "text": "that you were actively drinking, or even that the bottle cap was"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21160.0,
      "end_time": 22800.0,
      "text": "off."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22800.0,
      "end_time": 24830.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s enough if the bottle has been opened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24830.0,
      "end_time": 29580.0,
      "text": "the seal was broken, and it was either partially or entirely"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29580.0,
      "end_time": 30990.0,
      "text": "consumed."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30990.0,
      "end_time": 34780.0,
      "text": "An open container violation is usually just an infraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34780.0,
      "end_time": 38000.0,
      "text": "That means it&#39;s not a crime, and the maximum penalty"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38000.0,
      "end_time": 40180.0,
      "text": "is a $250 fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40180.0,
      "end_time": 42210.0,
      "text": "Although, with penalty and court costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42210.0,
      "end_time": 44950.0,
      "text": "that could be closer to a thousand dollars out the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44950.0,
      "end_time": 48370.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not a crime unless you&#39;re underage."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48370.0,
      "end_time": 52000.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re under 21, and you&#39;re driving with an open container,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52000.0,
      "end_time": 53700.0,
      "text": "then it&#39;s a misdemeanor."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53700.0,
      "end_time": 57270.0,
      "text": "And as such, it could carry up to six months in county jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57270.0,
      "end_time": 59210.0,
      "text": "But under any scenario, it will add points"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59210.0,
      "end_time": 61950.0,
      "text": "to your driving record, and almost certainly"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61950.0,
      "end_time": 64500.0,
      "text": "increase your insurance premiums."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64500.0,
      "end_time": 66640.0,
      "text": "Now a lot of people ask me, if I go out to dinner"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66640.0,
      "end_time": 69660.0,
      "text": "and I have a bottle of wine, and let&#39;s say we finish half of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69660.0,
      "end_time": 71259.0,
      "text": "I want to bring it home."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73630.0,
      "text": "Is that illegal to carry it in the car?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73630.0,
      "end_time": 75539.0,
      "text": "The answer is, in those situations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75540.0,
      "end_time": 78560.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re allowed to have an open container, as long as it&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78560.0,
      "end_time": 83700.0,
      "text": "in the trunk or a part of the vehicle not normally occupied"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83700.0,
      "end_time": 85720.0,
      "text": "by passengers, such as the bed of a pickup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85720.0,
      "end_time": 87420.0,
      "text": "or a locked container."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87420.0,
      "end_time": 90270.0,
      "text": "Now keep in mind that the glove compartment or a utility"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90270.0,
      "end_time": 92810.0,
      "text": "compartment generally do not count."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92810.0,
      "end_time": 95220.0,
      "text": "Moreover, the open container laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95220.0,
      "end_time": 98230.0,
      "text": "do not apply to buses, taxis, limousines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98230.0,
      "end_time": 100460.0,
      "text": "house cars, and campers."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100460.0,
      "end_time": 104970.0,
      "text": "Passengers in these types of vehicles, or for hire vehicles"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104970.0,
      "end_time": 107000.0,
      "text": "are allowed to have open containers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107000.0,
      "end_time": 109410.0,
      "text": "but the drivers are not."
    }
  ]
}